$version Hand-crafted Nexys Video vector fixture $end
$comment 8-bit LEDs vector, 8-bit switches vector, individual buttons, OLED MOSI, HDMI in/out 24-bit pixel data, 16-bit audio sample. Tests the auto-bind service's vector fan-out tier across the led / sw families and validates singleton-slot binding. $end
$date 2026-05-04 $end
$timescale 1ns $end
$scope module top $end
$var wire 8 ! leds $end
$var wire 8 " sws $end
$var wire 1 # btnC $end
$var wire 1 $ btnU $end
$var wire 1 % btnL $end
$var wire 1 & btnR $end
$var wire 1 ' btnD $end
$var wire 1 ( oled_mosi $end
$var wire 24 ) hdmi_in_data $end
$var wire 24 * hdmi_out_data $end
$var wire 16 + audio_left $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
